        <span class="author"><span>Written by </span><a href="https://www.adambowie.com/blog/author/adambowie/" title="Posts by adambowie" rel="author">adambowie</a><span class="divider">&bull;</span></span>        <span class="post-date">October 4, 2009<span class="divider">&bull;</span></span>
        <span class="categs"><a href="https://www.adambowie.com/blog/category/media/" rel="category tag">Media</a>, <a href="https://www.adambowie.com/blog/category/misc/" rel="category tag">Misc</a></span>
